Package: SGPCA
Title: Sparse Group Principal Component Analysis via Double Thresholding
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Qi", "Xu", , "qixu@andrew.cmu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1127-6523"))
Description: This package has two main functionalities: 1. estimate leading principal components with simultaneous group and individual sparsity. 2. select sparsity tuning parameter via a resampling-based method.
